                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991204-1-off1 t17991204-1-cd2"></join> a cambric handkerchief, value 2s. a lawn handkerchief, value 2s. and two muslin, handkerchiefs, value 2s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17991204-1-victim54" type="victimName">
